  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749505649-60QI8BGVP9YE8JKSA7F2/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>One of the best parts of living in Southern California is that a little beach getaway sometimes simply means taking a little break from work instead of missing a whole entire day of it. The accessibility of being able to drive just 15 minutes to a beach to spend less than an hour there is something I do not take for granted. On days or weeks when there is just so much going on, escaping just for a little time by the ocean can do wonders. <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?B=286192&amp;U=530666&amp;M=31374&amp;urllink=\">Cents of Style</a> sent over <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=286192&amp;m=31374&amp;afftrack=roundie&amp;urllink=www%2Emycentsofstyle%2Ecom%2Fproducts%2Fclassic%2Dflamingo%2Dbeach%2Dblanket\">this Classic Flamingo Beach Blanket</a>, and I couldn't think of anything better than to take a little break from a hectic day/week/month/year for some time on the sand.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"9b-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749531032-ND2B220JZX6CD73H5S0A/9b-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"9c-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749530872-Z9QY7Z1AJLD895QJ8Q73/9c-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9d-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749532729-U95WUBYVUV5XQBXEPELJ/9d-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9e-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749533514-5KR1BMJ9ONO96R61A3D9/9e-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9f-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749534028-YNCSCXBZIAKVUGWLZ8EH/9f-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9g-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749535782-KQ3U1TTIUPOVJ60BP8AI/9g-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9h-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749536512-FUM10ZUQTEAPSYMS3XJS/9h-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9i-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749537417-OR0GMFDVR49KEMLDM4U7/9i-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9j-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749538638-TWP04K7ED8IGJXI7S7G6/9j-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9k-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749539663-JR1PSFFU4ZO8XGMU04QC/9k-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9l-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595749541026-ZXWWJD1G6JJBKVAPN2PC/9l-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=286192&amp;m=31374&amp;afftrack=roundie&amp;urllink=www%2Emycentsofstyle%2Ecom%2Fproducts%2Fclassic%2Dflamingo%2Dbeach%2Dblanket\">The beach blanket/wrap</a> is lightweight and lovely. It was hard choosing from all the awesome prints, but I figured you could never go wrong with some flamingos! Plus, through the weekend, the round towels are just $21.95 with the code: STORYTHROW (sorry for the correction - the beach wraps are $15.95 using the same code).</p><p><em>Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>"
